e Max, Disney+, Hulu bundle. But I agree that unless he ditches the =E2=80=
=9Cadjusted EBITDA=E2=80=9D crutch and starts hitting those projections, he=
 will be in a bigger mess than he already finds himself.  <br/><br/>In the =
meantime, every little thing Zaz does gets scrutinized and criticized, perh=
aps justly, from the H=C3=B4tel de Crillon stay at the Paris
