nk Zaz is barking up the wrong tree with the NBA lawsuit, and that it=E2=80=
=99s just an attempt to save face after blowing the negotiation. On the oth=
er hand, Matt, if WBD doesn=E2=80=99t have the NBA, that frees up something=
